  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Way Of Heaven
---
Confucius said, "To be glad and joyful  in mind; to embrace universal
love and be without partisanship - this is the true form of benevolence
and righteousness."
